THAT THE VERY EARTH
WOULD CRACK OPEN

38:29.667 --> 38:32.708
AND CAPESIDE WOULD BECOME
HOME TO A HUGE HELLMOUTH

38:32.708 --> 38:36.667
THAT WOULD SPEW FORTH
ENDLESS HORDES OF
MONSTERS AND DEMONS

38:36.667 --> 38:38.959
THAT WOULD CHOKE
THE DENIZENS OF THE CITY,

38:38.959 --> 38:41.125
MAKING THEM FALL
TO THEIR KNEES

38:41.125 --> 38:44.583
AND PRAY FOR A RETURN
TO THE DAYS BEFORE
I TOOK ACTION.

38:44.583 --> 38:46.750
THAT'S REALLY WHAT
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT HERE.

38:46.750 --> 38:49.291
HUH.

38:49.291 --> 38:50.959
YEAH, MAYBE...

38:54.583 --> 38:57.291
LOOK, PACEY, UH...
AHEM.

38:58.291 --> 38:59.834
IN MY EXPERIENCE,

38:59.834 --> 39:02.000
YOU DON'T COME ACROSS
THAT MANY PEOPLE

39:02.000 --> 39:03.917
WITH THE ABILITY
TO GIVE YOU BUTTERFLIES.

39:03.917 --> 39:07.000
YOU JUST DON'T.

39:07.000 --> 39:10.500
AND IF YOU DON'T
TELL THIS GIRL
HOW YOU FEEL,

39:10.500 --> 39:13.458
WELL, IT'LL BE LIKE
SPENDING THE REST
OF YOUR LIFE

39:13.458 --> 39:14.500
IN YOUR OWN PERSONAL
PRISON.

39:16.750 --> 39:18.000
HEY, DOUG?

39:18.000 --> 39:20.625
YEAH.

39:20.625 --> 39:23.208
THANK YOU.

