WAS WAY OUTTA LINE.

40:20.708 --> 40:23.834
AND...YES, I WAS DRUNK,

40:23.834 --> 40:27.583
BUT...MORE TO THE POINT,
I WAS JUST PLAIN WRONG.

40:27.583 --> 40:31.417
AND I WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT I'M REALLY SORRY.

40:32.917 --> 40:35.458
WELL...

40:35.458 --> 40:38.083
