ABOUT YOU, TOO,
PACEY.

40:39.750 --> 40:40.708
ME?

40:42.125 --> 40:43.458
WHY?

40:45.000 --> 40:46.834
WELL...

40:48.500 --> 40:50.125
BECAUSE, I MEAN,

40:50.125 --> 40:53.708
SATAN HIMSELF COULD LEAD
DAWSON INTO THE FIERY
PITS OF HELL,

40:53.708 --> 40:56.750
AND HE WOULD STILL EMERGE
WITH HIS MORAL CODE
FIRMLY INTACT.

40:56.750 --> 40:57.542
BUT YOU...

41:01.542 --> 41:03.583
MAYBE I THINK THAT...

41:03.583 --> 41:06.083
NOBODY'S WORRYING
ABOUT YOU RIGHT NOW.

41:09.667 --> 41:11.250
SO, THEN...AHEM.

41:11.250 --> 41:13.750
WHAT YOU'RE REALLY
SAYING, THEN,
IS THAT...

41:13.750 --> 41:16.458
GIVEN THE HIGHLY
DYSFUNCTIONAL NATURE
OF OUR RELATIONSHIP,

41:16.458 --> 41:19.458
THIS IS ACTUALLY
HOW YOU EXPRESS
CONCERN FOR ME.

41:19.458 --> 41:22.333
YOU GOTTA LEARN TO READ
BETWEEN THE BANTER, PACEY.

41:24.959 --> 41:26.375
RIGHT.

41:34.375 --> 41:35.959
SO...

41:35.959 --> 41:38.333
SO ARE WE
ALL FINISHED HERE?

41:38.333 --> 41:40.041
NO.

41:40.041 --> 41:41.458
ACTUALLY. UM...

41:41.458 --> 41:44.333
THERE'S SOMETHING
ELSE.

41:44.333 --> 41:46.750
SOMETHING ELSE?

41:48.500 --> 41:49.750
YEAH.

41:51.834 --> 41:54.083
IT'S--IT'S JUST
SOMETHING I'VE BEEN
MEANING TO TELL YOU.

41:54.083 --> 41:57.708
UH...

41:59.834 --> 42:01.500
LOOK, UH...

42:03.917 --> 42:05.333
JOEY...

42:10.000 --> 42:11.834
YOU'RE LINGERING
ON YOUR CLUTCH, OK?

42:11.834 --> 42:13.959
I KNOW YOU THINK
YOU'RE JUST EASING
INTO THE GEAR,

42:13.959 --> 42:16.291
BUT...IT'S NOT
A GOOD IDEA.

42:16.291 --> 42:18.250
MAYBE NOT TODAY
AND MAYBE NOT
TOMORROW,

42:18.250 --> 42:20.041
BUT SOON YOU'RE GONNA
DO A LOTTA DAMAGE
TO YOUR TRANSMISSION,

42:20.041 --> 42:23.125
SO WHAT I WAS THINKING
IF THAT IF YOU WANTED
TO, I COULD SHOW YA.

42:23.125 --> 42:25.166
NOW?

42:26.875 --> 42:27.959
YEAH.

42:27.959 --> 42:29.708
YEAH. HA.

42:29.708 --> 42:31.458
OK, PACEY.

42:31.458 --> 42:31.708
OK.

42:35.083 --> 42:36.125
NOW?

42:36.125 --> 42:37.125
NOT NOW.

42:37.125 --> 42:38.166
NOW?

42:38.166 --> 42:40.917
NOW! SHIFT!

42:40.917 --> 42:42.166
HUH?

42:42.166 --> 42:43.333
HUH?!

42:43.333 --> 42:44.250
I DID IT!

42:44.250 --> 42:45.834
YES, YOU DID!
HA HA!

42:45.834 --> 42:47.208
CONGRATULATIONS,
POTTER.

42:47.208 --> 42:48.875
WE ARE FINALLY
GETTIN' SOMEWHERE.

